Package: flowregime
Title: Environmental Flow Regime Indicators
Version: 0.7.0.9000
Date: 2016-04-15
Author: Michael C Koohafkan [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Michael C Koohafkan <michael.koohafkan@gmail.com>
Description: Compute environmental flow indicators from hydrologic time series.
    Designed to work with 'xts' objects. Defines functions for computing flow 
    indicators such as time to rise, time to fall and days above/below a flow 
    threshold. Also implements the Indicators of Hydrologic Alteration (IHA).
URL: https://github.com/mkoohafkan/flowregime
BugReports: https://github.com/mkoohafkan/flowregime/issues
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0),
    stats,
    utils,
    xts (>= 0.9-7)
Imports:
    zoo (>= 1.7-12)
Suggests:
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
